WEBVTT

00:00:36.018 --> 00:00:38.527
MY NAME IS NAOMI LOEBEL.

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:42.773
I AM INTERVIEWING SURVIVOR NAMED SARAH TAUB.

00:00:42.773 --> 00:00:44.368
BORN SALAMON.

00:00:44.368 --> 00:00:48.292
THE DATE IS FEBRUARY TWENTY-SIX, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN.

00:00:48.292 --> 00:00:50.407
WE ARE IN JERUSALEM, ISRAEL.

00:00:55.036 --> 00:00:56.870
vos iz ayer nomen?

00:00:59.643 --> 00:01:00.769
Sara.

00:01:01.533 --> 00:01:03.064
di letste nomen?

00:01:03.895 --> 00:01:04.869
vi azoy?

00:01:04.908 --> 00:01:07.249
vi azoy nokh heyst ir?

00:01:08.755 --> 00:01:10.134
Sara Toyb.

00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:14.676
vos iz geven ayer nomen ven ir zent geboyrn?

00:01:14.668 --> 00:01:15.757
Solomon.

00:01:18.020 --> 00:01:20.158
hot ir gehat an andere nomen?

00:01:22.437 --> 00:01:24.277
neyn.

00:01:24.348 --> 00:01:26.317
ven zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:26.755 --> 00:01:31.451
in yare nayn toyznt elef.

00:01:33.224 --> 00:01:35.666
vi alt zen ir haynt?

00:01:36.717 --> 00:01:38.653
haynt bin ikh,

00:01:39.670 --> 00:01:43.125
in ferdn, bin ikh gevorn,

00:01:44.311 --> 00:01:47.225
februar ferde bin ikh gevorn

00:01:47.332 --> 00:01:52.035
finef un zekhtsik. finef un akhtsik yor.

00:01:55.027 --> 00:01:57.874
in velkhe shtot zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:58.674 --> 00:01:59.448
vi azoy?

00:01:59.350 --> 00:02:01.588
in velkhe shtot zent ir geboyrn?

00:02:01.489 --> 00:02:06.548
ikh bin geboyrn in a dorf, dos dorf heyst Ardusat.

00:02:08.232 --> 00:02:10.213
un vu iz dos gevezn?

00:02:10.349 --> 00:02:18.985
deys iz geven in um, nisht vayt fun Sakmer.

00:02:19.006 --> 00:02:20.570
in velkhe land?

00:02:20.795 --> 00:02:21.650
Rumenye.

00:02:24.204 --> 00:02:27.270
vi azoy hobn geheysn ayere eltern?

00:02:28.996 --> 00:02:31.196
 mishpokhe?

00:02:31.196 --> 00:02:33.227
eltern, di tate un di mame.

00:02:32.270 --> 00:02:33.007
yo, yo, yo.

00:02:33.249 --> 00:02:36.264
ober, oykh mishpokhe?

00:02:35.764 --> 00:02:37.108
ale, ale nemen.

00:02:37.113 --> 00:02:37.827
yo.

00:02:37.827 --> 00:02:42.424
di mame hot geheysn Vaysner, Sheyndl.

00:02:42.530 --> 00:02:46.541
der tate hot geheysn Sholomon, Binyomen.

00:02:48.318 --> 00:02:50.912
velkhe land zenen zey geboyrn?

00:02:50.907 --> 00:02:52.942
oykh in Rumenye.

00:02:54.393 --> 00:02:57.037
ir hot gehat shvesters un briders?

00:02:57.877 --> 00:02:59.197
ver di mame?

00:02:59.167 --> 00:02:59.905
neyn, ir.

00:02:59.967 --> 00:03:00.660
yo.

00:03:01.261 --> 00:03:03.332
vi azoy hobn zey geheysn?

00:03:04.450 --> 00:03:10.790
der groyser bruder hot geheysn Yankl.

00:03:11.622 --> 00:03:14.047
der tsveyter, Yosl.

00:03:14.727 --> 00:03:19.852
un di shvester hot geheysn Brayndl,

00:03:20.853 --> 00:03:28.054
un nokh di shvester hot geheysn di tsveyte shvester B-, Berta.

00:03:29.189 --> 00:03:31.445
un dernokh dem kum ikh.

00:03:32.244 --> 00:03:34.837
un nokh mi-, ikh, Sara.

00:03:35.028 --> 00:03:41.570
nokh mir, iz geven a Malkele. Ma-, Maltshi.

00:03:44.562 --> 00:03:47.359
un a yingele Moyshe.

00:03:48.714 --> 00:04:02.394
un dernokh dem iz geven a yingele Zanvele, Mordkhele, un shoyn.

00:04:04.779 --> 00:04:09.769
velkhe shprakh hobn ay- hobn ir geredt in shtub?

00:04:10.752 --> 00:04:13.882
velkhe shparn me hot geredt di shtub?

00:04:12.845 --> 00:04:14.380
velkhe shprakh, shprakh...

00:04:14.110 --> 00:04:18.375
yidish. a bisele oykh ungarish.

00:04:14.933 --> 00:04:15.798
yidish?

00:04:19.105 --> 00:04:22.273
un in droysn fun di shtub, vi azoy hot men geredt?

00:04:23.392 --> 00:04:27.403
ober rumenish, ober ungarish.

00:04:29.639 --> 00:04:35.182
vifl mentshn hobn gevoynt in in di dorf vu ir zent geboyrn?

00:04:36.419 --> 00:04:45.712
nisht a ikh meyn oykh yidn, oykh goyim, fir hundert.

00:04:47.557 --> 00:04:49.104
in vifl yidn?

00:04:50.071 --> 00:04:51.129
veynik.

00:04:52.417 --> 00:04:59.602
yidn iz geven beerekh fuftsn mishpokhes. tsvelef.

00:05:00.316 --> 00:05:02.639
fuftsn, azoy gatung.

00:05:03.335 --> 00:05:07.076
ir kent a bisl dertseyln vegn di lebn in di dorf

00:05:09.457 --> 00:05:10.516
vi azoy?

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:12.527
ir kent a bisl dertseyln

00:05:12.565 --> 00:05:15.767
vegn, vi azoy di lebn iz geven in di dorf.

00:05:15.991 --> 00:05:19.235
vi azoy hobn di mentshn dort ge- zikh

00:05:19.178 --> 00:05:20.531
zeyer shver.

00:05:21.604 --> 00:05:26.314
se iz nisht keyn raykher dorf.

00:05:27.685 --> 00:05:29.689
un me hot shver gelebt.

00:05:31.179 --> 00:05:36.860
se iz geven shve- far di yidn shvakhe parnose,

00:05:36.916 --> 00:05:42.971
di goyim hobn ge-, beser gelebt a bisl, zey hobn gehat erd.

00:05:42.971 --> 00:05:45.163
un zey hobn gearbet di erd.

00:05:45.691 --> 00:05:49.669
un di yidn hobn gemakht BUSINESS

00:05:50.922 --> 00:05:53.533
vos far a sort BUSINESS hobn zey gemakht?

00:05:54.247 --> 00:05:55.946
sokhreray.

00:05:57.065 --> 00:06:03.135
lemoshl, mayn tate iz gevezn a katsev.

00:06:03.967 --> 00:06:05.902
ir veyst vos iz katsev?

00:06:06.886 --> 00:06:15.960
un se iz geven tsvey yidn hobn gehat a shnitseray gesheft.

00:06:16.606 --> 00:06:22.322
eyn yid hot gehat a gesheft fun, shtofn.

00:06:23.778 --> 00:06:30.607
eyn yid hot gehat a verk-shtub fun, mantlen, shnayderay.

00:06:30.781 --> 00:06:32.700
mantlen, antsug,

00:06:36.552 --> 00:06:40.564
un epes andersh denk ikh nisht.

00:06:43.015 --> 00:06:48.005
un ayer mishpokhe iz geven um, frum?

00:06:48.837 --> 00:06:51.515
bayn undz iz nisht geven keyn fraye yidn.

00:06:53.022 --> 00:07:00.544
nor se iz geven in in dorf a dokter, a yid,

00:07:00.599 --> 00:07:05.809
ober der hot gornisht gevolt visn fun yidishkeyt.

00:07:07.518 --> 00:07:09.892
ayer tate iz geven a khosid?

00:07:10.437 --> 00:07:12.862
yo, a satmerer khosid.

00:07:13.458 --> 00:07:15.799
er iz gegangen a mol tsu di rebe?

00:07:17.097 --> 00:07:17.934
vi azoy?

00:07:17.885 --> 00:07:19.916
er flegt geyn tsu di rebe?

00:07:19.887 --> 00:07:20.507
yo.

00:07:23.431 --> 00:07:25.687
ikh denk nisht BEDIYUK,

00:07:25.878 --> 00:07:29.619
in Sakmer iz er gegangen, dos gedenk ikh,

00:07:30.704 --> 00:07:34.175
un nokh ergets iz er gegangen,

00:07:34.889 --> 00:07:38.749
dakht zikh mir in Bukovine.

00:07:40.728 --> 00:07:43.659
ober ikh bin nisht azoy shtark zikher.

00:07:43.816 --> 00:07:46.595
deys veys ikh, az in Sakmer.

00:07:49.419 --> 00:07:53.514
vos iz geven di bashefigung fun ayer tate?

00:07:53.941 --> 00:07:54.898
katsev

00:07:54.954 --> 00:07:58.813
v- vos meynt dos, vos hot er gebroykht tsu tun?

00:07:59.358 --> 00:08:02.424
er hot gelozt shekhtn di beheymes

00:08:02.024 --> 00:08:03.319
di beheyme,

00:08:03.897 --> 00:08:05.715
un er hot zey

00:08:06.445 --> 00:08:08.044
mit a mentsh,

00:08:08.065 --> 00:08:10.507
un er hot zey opgeshindn,

00:08:10.884 --> 00:08:15.131
un er hot zey tseteylt, di beheyme, in tsveyen.

00:08:15.204 --> 00:08:18.439
vos di hintershte zayt iz treyfe.

00:08:19.034 --> 00:08:23.839
un di ershte zayt hot er getreybert. gereynikt.

00:08:25.345 --> 00:08:31.078
un dernokh dem, hot er es, oysgemostn

00:08:31.285 --> 00:08:35.989
ver vifl hot gevolt, a kilo, tsvey kilo, halbe kilo,

00:08:36.449 --> 00:08:38.358
vifl me hot gevolt.

00:08:40.854 --> 00:08:42.201
ayer mame hot oykh

00:08:42.201 --> 00:08:44.403
gea- geholfn in dey gesheft?

00:08:44.403 --> 00:08:45.017
neyn.

00:08:47.755 --> 00:08:53.910
mayn mame iz farnumen gevezn mit di kinder.

00:08:56.514 --> 00:08:57.791
ir kent

00:08:58.134 --> 00:09:02.229
dertseyln vi azoy se iz geven shabes in ayer shtub?

00:09:05.272 --> 00:09:08.608
dos, shoyn a bisl shver.

00:09:09.423 --> 00:09:18.142
dos veys ikh, se iz geven gebentsht,

00:09:18.687 --> 00:09:24.049
geshtelt aher a groyser ⟨makazh⟩ mit likht.

00:09:24.442 --> 00:09:28.655
dos veys ikh, se iz geven nayn likht, dos denk ikh.

00:09:30.129 --> 00:09:35.102
un in yener zayt iz geven di khales.

00:09:36.980 --> 00:09:40.940
un do iz geven in mitn di flash mitn vayn.

00:09:43.477 --> 00:09:45.615
un der beker.

00:09:45.873 --> 00:09:49.125
un oyf di zaytn iz geven di telers.

00:09:53.484 --> 00:09:56.094
un kanen mit vaser.

00:10:01.550 --> 00:10:04.005
di khales hot men aleyn gebakn?

00:10:04.053 --> 00:10:04.561
yo.

00:10:06.764 --> 00:10:08.902
dos oykh khales,

00:10:08.975 --> 00:10:10.607
oykh broyt,

00:10:11.658 --> 00:10:15.720
oykh milkhike UGA.

00:10:23.032 --> 00:10:29.557
vi azoy iz geven dort far peysekh? vos vos iz forgegangen in ayer shtub?

00:10:29.835 --> 00:10:30.608
vi azoy?

00:10:30.636 --> 00:10:32.072
far peysekh,

00:10:32.397 --> 00:10:36.307
vos iz forgegangen in ayer shtub? vi azoy hot men zikh ongegreyt?

00:10:36.954 --> 00:10:40.256
far peysekh iz geven a groyser ruml.

00:10:42.219 --> 00:10:49.301
koydem, me hot gebroykht iberal zeyer reyn makhn.

00:10:51.264 --> 00:10:59.527
un arop, shteln hantekher vu me shtelt dos geshir,

00:11:01.169 --> 00:11:05.484
un me hot gebroykht, nu, deys geshir

00:11:05.574 --> 00:11:07.222
deys khometsike,

00:11:07.531 --> 00:11:14.040
hot men gebroykht aroyftrogn oyf a boydem. in a kastn.

00:11:14.922 --> 00:11:21.178
un aropgebrengt, aropgenumen dos peysekhike.

00:11:23.208 --> 00:11:26.730
ven men hot aropgenumen dos peysekhike geshir,

00:11:26.920 --> 00:11:30.358
hot men aropgenumen oykh di matses.

00:11:32.455 --> 00:11:41.209
un oykh, se iz geven avekgeton, ven der sezon iz geven fun zoyere zakhn,

00:11:41.922 --> 00:11:44.938
hot men gemakht zoyere ⟨inmorkn⟩

00:11:45.449 --> 00:11:50.051
zoyer gemakht mit zoy- mit grine troybn,

00:11:51.204 --> 00:11:54.034
in aroyfgeshtelt oyfn boydem.

00:11:54.697 --> 00:11:58.742
un ven me hot aropgenumen dos peysekhike geshir,

00:11:59.118 --> 00:12:06.487
un di ma- dem kastn mit di matses, vayl matses hot men gebakn kol.

00:12:07.775 --> 00:12:19.903
a yederer hot ge- hot gehat mel, gemakht gekashert di mil,

00:12:20.262 --> 00:12:22.282
un me hot gemakht mel,

00:12:22.557 --> 00:12:28.256
un dem veyts fun vos me hot gemakht dos mel,

00:12:28.700 --> 00:12:36.592
hot men geton oyf tishn, oyf oyf zoybere tishtekh,

00:12:37.576 --> 00:12:41.520
un azoy oysgeveylt a vi rayz.

00:12:42.031 --> 00:12:44.237
vi azoy me kloybt di rayz.

00:12:44.495 --> 00:12:46.734
azoy iz geven bayn undz.

00:12:48.528 --> 00:12:56.336
un erev peysekh hot men gemakht shmire matses.

00:12:56.746 --> 00:12:59.376
un me hot gemakht matses,

00:12:59.376 --> 00:13:03.761
shtots vaser, vegn mezoynes,

00:13:03.817 --> 00:13:06.090
hot men gemakht mit ayer.

00:13:07.546 --> 00:13:08.115
dos

00:13:10.887 --> 00:13:13.970
dos hot geheysn ayer matses.

00:13:15.460 --> 00:13:18.527
un dos iz geven zeyer opgehit,

00:13:19.038 --> 00:13:29.428
nisht kholile se zol tsukumen oyf epes a nase zakh.

00:13:30.344 --> 00:13:32.584
oyf, nisht nas, faykht.

00:13:36.672 --> 00:13:45.139
un bayn undz in shtub iz nisht geven peysekh keyn matse mel.

00:13:46.797 --> 00:13:48.547
nor um,

00:13:51.944 --> 00:13:53.509
vi azoy heyst es?

00:13:55.555 --> 00:13:57.322
kartofl mel.

00:13:57.732 --> 00:14:01.659
un di kartofl mel ho'mir undz gemakht aleyn.

00:14:04.297 --> 00:14:06.654
zeyer a groyse arbet.

00:14:08.094 --> 00:14:10.721
dos hot men nisht gemakht in shtub.

00:14:15.468 --> 00:14:18.737
me hot geton, in droysn, in KATSER,

00:14:22.150 --> 00:14:28.794
in geshir vos me broykh tsu dem, deys hot dokh geshir,

00:14:29.137 --> 00:14:40.337
un azoy hot men gemakht di matse me-, di di kartofl mel.

00:14:40.696 --> 00:14:46.648
zalts ho'mir gehat aza proste mashin

00:14:47.058 --> 00:14:56.216
mit shteyn, un der tate zol zikh mien hot gebrengt groys shtik zalts,

00:14:57.031 --> 00:15:01.751
un ge- ayngetsundn dem oyvn, vi me makht broyt,

00:15:03.629 --> 00:15:07.725
un ahin arayngeton dos zalts,

00:15:08.860 --> 00:15:11.724
un dos hot zikh dort oysgebrent,

00:15:12.033 --> 00:15:15.605
un nokh dem hot men es aroysgenumen, opgekilt,

00:15:16.066 --> 00:15:17.647
un tsebrokhn,

00:15:18.445 --> 00:15:21.326
un arayngeton in der mil,

00:15:21.719 --> 00:15:27.097
oyf der mil hot men gornisht gemakht, oyf dem shteyn.

00:15:27.339 --> 00:15:33.274
nor vi azoy heyst es? nor zalts.

00:15:34.713 --> 00:15:41.610
un di zalts hot men gebroykht oysfenen, vi azoy me fent mel.

00:15:42.880 --> 00:15:47.837
un vos se iz untergefaln, dos iz geven UNK oyfn tish.

00:15:48.601 --> 00:15:56.089
un vos iz oyvn geven, dos iz geven UNK kosher makhn. ober dos iz geven fun yor oyf yor.

00:15:56.414 --> 00:16:05.285
UNK bayn undz hot men khanike gemakht peysekhik zalts, um, shmalts.

00:16:05.746 --> 00:16:08.222
bayn undz iz nisht geven keyn shemen.

00:16:09.357 --> 00:16:14.449
un di shmalts ho'mir undz gemakht gendz, me hot geshtopt gendz,

00:16:14.622 --> 00:16:18.920
un fun dem hot men gemakht dos fleysh,

00:16:19.465 --> 00:16:22.295
un di di shmalts.

00:16:23.094 --> 00:16:31.087
un fleysh iz geven oykh in, fun tate, fun fun tatn's gesheft.

00:16:31.717 --> 00:16:35.576
un mit dem zalts vos iz geblibn in di

00:16:36.459 --> 00:16:40.419
se iz spetsyel geven ⟨ven⟩ kosher tsu makhn.

00:16:41.015 --> 00:16:48.013
un dos halbe dorf iz gekumen tsu undz nemen zalts.

00:16:52.608 --> 00:16:54.628
vos zol ikh nokh zogn?

00:16:56.675 --> 00:17:06.038
vi azoy iz geven in in di dorf di ongeyn mit di goyim, vi azoy hobn zikh

00:17:06.038 --> 00:17:08.053
farnumen di goyim kegn di yidn?

00:17:08.003 --> 00:17:10.524
mit di yidn? demolts nokh gut.

00:17:10.900 --> 00:17:14.861
nor fun ven Hitler iz gekumen UNK,

00:17:15.271 --> 00:17:16.937
iz nisht geven gut.

00:17:17.380 --> 00:17:22.100
me hot ongefangen yidn tsu hargenen, un tsu avektraybn,

00:17:23.624 --> 00:17:26.150
in velkhe shule zent ir gegangen?

00:17:27.404 --> 00:17:28.564
Rumenish.

00:17:29.665 --> 00:17:31.534
vos hot men dort gelertnt?

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:35.769
keyn toyre zakhn.

00:17:37.765 --> 00:17:42.941
me hot gelernt shraybn, leyenen,

00:17:44.988 --> 00:17:46.755
nisht epes ekstere.

00:17:49.291 --> 00:17:55.310
vos hot men getun ven se iz nisht geven shul, vos hobn di kinder dort gesh- geshpilt?

00:17:56.767 --> 00:17:58.719
UNK

00:18:01.863 --> 00:18:08.895
lemoshl, ikh hob gelernt fun mayn babe hantarbet.

00:18:10.368 --> 00:18:17.214
bay, oyfn dorf, keyn yidishe kinder geyen nisht arum a vu do, hefker.

00:18:17.304 --> 00:18:20.684
shpiln FOOTBALL, un shlogn zikh un,

00:18:20.684 --> 00:18:21.990
se iz nisht do.

00:18:23.007 --> 00:18:26.293
un dernokh dem, me ho'mir gehat a kheyder.

00:18:26.686 --> 00:18:31.642
mayn tate hot gegen a plats vegn a kheyder, vu tsu...

00:18:31.968 --> 00:18:33.212
far mitog,

00:18:33.571 --> 00:18:38.983
ho'mir gelernt, nisht ale tog, ge- shul,

00:18:39.562 --> 00:18:43.624
un nokh mitog iz nisht geven ale tog shul,

00:18:44.202 --> 00:18:47.842
un, ze'mir gegangen, gelernt in kheyder.

00:18:47.949 --> 00:18:53.833
mir ze'mir fun nokh mitog aroysgegangen fun der shul,

00:18:54.564 --> 00:18:57.680
hot men gegangen in kheyder.

00:19:02.495 --> 00:19:06.928
i- ir gedenkt nokh fun ayer khavertes in di shul?

00:19:09.379 --> 00:19:10.036
neyn.

00:19:10.780 --> 00:19:14.066
koydem, ikh bin avek fun dorf,

00:19:18.442 --> 00:19:23.972
ikh veys vi alt ikh bin geven, draytsn, fertsn yor.

00:19:24.500 --> 00:19:26.520
bin ikh avek fun dort,

00:19:27.250 --> 00:19:29.591
ikh hob nisht gehat keyn heym.

00:19:32.195 --> 00:19:39.767
von, biz der tate hot gelebt iz nokh geven epes.

00:19:39.890 --> 00:19:45.605
ober ven der tate iz geshtorbn, ikh hot gehat z-, tsveyte mame.

00:19:45.661 --> 00:19:49.723
zi iz nisht geven gut, zi iz nisht geven a guter mentsh.

00:19:49.795 --> 00:19:52.406
ven der tate iz geven der heym,

00:19:52.411 --> 00:19:57.131
hot zi zikh oyfgefirt nisht geferlekh shlekht.

00:19:57.288 --> 00:20:00.348
ober ven der tate iz nisht geven in der heym,

00:20:00.348 --> 00:20:02.919
hot zi zikh nisht gut oyfgefirt.

00:20:04.747 --> 00:20:07.543
un ikh hob gehat seykhl, dertsu,

00:20:07.615 --> 00:20:12.926
ikh hob nisht gezogt farn tate vi azoy zi iz shlekht tsu mir.

00:20:13.724 --> 00:20:16.537
von, ikh hob nisht gevolt se zol zayn,

00:20:17.572 --> 00:20:20.604
in der shtub, nisht BESEDER.

00:20:22.904 --> 00:20:25.177
un se iz zeyer shver geven.

00:20:25.824 --> 00:20:27.574
zeyer shver geven.

00:20:29.958 --> 00:20:32.417
ven ir zent gegangen in di shul,

00:20:33.012 --> 00:20:37.766
vos hot ir geklert tsu tun ven ir vet oyfvaksn?

00:20:39.543 --> 00:20:42.609
ikh hob mikh farnumen, alts a kind,

00:20:43.306 --> 00:20:45.748
a kleyn kind, bayn shpiln,

00:20:45.972 --> 00:20:47.570
mit kokhn,

00:20:49.314 --> 00:20:52.363
nisht kokhn oyfn fayer,

00:20:54.393 --> 00:21:01.334
mit zayn a kranke shvester. dey tsvey MIKTSOE

00:21:01.334 --> 00:21:04.175
hob ikh mikh nor mit dem geshpilt.

00:21:04.501 --> 00:21:07.314
andere meydelekh hobn zikh geshpilt,

00:21:07.387 --> 00:21:09.637
zey hobn gemakht a BUBE,

00:21:09.637 --> 00:21:14.149
zey hobn gemakht kleynikeytn, ober ikh nisht.

00:21:14.575 --> 00:21:17.405
un nebekh, mayn babe,

00:21:17.832 --> 00:21:20.848
hot gezogt az ikh bin shoyn,

00:21:20.971 --> 00:21:23.514
alts kleynervayz oys,

00:21:23.654 --> 00:21:28.003
az ikh farnem mikh mit ernste zakhn.

00:21:29.037 --> 00:21:35.867
un azoy iz es geven, ikh hob mikh mit ernste zakhn farnumen ad-hayom.

00:21:38.589 --> 00:21:47.764
vi azoy iz geven dos lebn ven Hitler iz oyfgeshtanen, in nayntsn dray un draysik?

00:21:47.954 --> 00:21:50.143
ikh bin nisht dort geven.

00:21:50.739 --> 00:21:51.628
ven

00:21:53.185 --> 00:21:55.307
azoy ven, onfang,

00:21:55.480 --> 00:22:01.550
hobn di goyim ongefangen tsu zayn antisemitn.

00:22:03.429 --> 00:22:06.748
ober ven Hitler iz shoyn

00:22:07.394 --> 00:22:12.975
oyf di fis geshtelt, ikh bin nisht geven dort. vayl dort iz azoy geven,

00:22:13.132 --> 00:22:16.839
ven ikh bin geboyrn, iz geven Ungarn.

00:22:17.637 --> 00:22:22.054
ober nisht a sakh tsayt. nisht a sakh yorn.

00:22:22.312 --> 00:22:25.817
nokh dem iz gevorn Rumenye.

00:22:27.695 --> 00:22:30.069
yo, yo. Rumenye.

00:22:30.867 --> 00:22:36.600
un nokh dem, ven Hitler iz ongefangen kumen tsu koyekh,

00:22:36.824 --> 00:22:40.127
iz geve- gevorn viderum Ungarn.

00:22:40.874 --> 00:22:45.715
un ven se iz geven shoyn dos tsveyte mol tsurik Ungarn,

00:22:45.715 --> 00:22:49.830
iz shoyn zeyer biter geven. zeyer biter.

00:22:51.674 --> 00:23:00.225
ikh hob gehat a shvester, nebekh, di klenere shvester mayne, mit zeks kinder.

00:23:00.483 --> 00:23:02.942
un se iz gekumen an ungar,

00:23:03.622 --> 00:23:07.262
un er hot zey aroysgevorfn fun ir shtub,

00:23:07.807 --> 00:23:09.827
un zi hot gevoynt,

00:23:10.017 --> 00:23:16.830
zi hot nebekh, er hot zey arayngeshtelt in a kleyn, kleyn kamerl.

00:23:17.358 --> 00:23:21.335
vos fir kinder zenen geshlofn in eyn bet.

00:23:21.999 --> 00:23:25.352
un zi iz in an andern bet geshlofn,

00:23:25.627 --> 00:23:29.756
ober zeyer shver hot di betn plats gehat.

00:23:31.449 --> 00:23:35.544
un se iz geven erger vi shlekht.

00:23:36.393 --> 00:23:40.387
un dernokh dem hot zikh ongefangen di deportirn.

00:23:42.687 --> 00:23:45.821
ikh, ikh bin oyfgevaksn,

00:23:46.653 --> 00:23:52.622
hob ikh mikh farnumen mit a bisl sokhreray.

00:23:54.854 --> 00:23:57.600
un ikh hob mir tsamgeb-,

00:23:57.723 --> 00:23:59.743
ikh hob mikh basheftikt,

00:24:00.828 --> 00:24:11.066
ikh hob gebrengt fun Tshekhay, fun Slovakay, farshidene zakhn.

00:24:12.708 --> 00:24:18.879
un ikh hob, in Rumenye dos zeyer gut farkoyft. un kh'hob sheyn gelt fardint.

00:24:19.171 --> 00:24:26.405
un ikh hob mir gekoyft a sakh shtafir, ikh hob dokh nisht gehat fun vemen tsu vartn.

00:24:27.102 --> 00:24:30.084
oykh ikh, oykh an andere shvester,

00:24:30.511 --> 00:24:36.311
azoy az dey, kh'hob gehat tsvey groyse kastn mit zakhn.

00:24:36.822 --> 00:24:39.062
un, nisht kleydung.

00:24:40.788 --> 00:24:45.997
ibertsikhn, tishtekher, azolekhike zakhn,

00:24:47.133 --> 00:24:56.021
un se iz gekumen zeyer a shlekhter ungarisher, un er hot genumen ale zakhn,

00:24:56.448 --> 00:25:00.324
un avekge-, avekgenumen far zikh.

00:25:01.409 --> 00:25:04.020
deys iz geven bay mayn shvester.

00:25:04.109 --> 00:25:06.889
ober di zakhn zenen mayn geven.

00:25:08.581 --> 00:25:17.014
un azoy hob ikh gehat iberbet, un farshidene zakhn, oykh bay mayn shvester,

00:25:17.221 --> 00:25:19.342
oyvn oyfn boydem.

00:25:19.432 --> 00:25:21.890
geton oyf azoy a shtang.

00:25:24.528 --> 00:25:26.160
ales avekgenumen.

00:25:26.283 --> 00:25:28.995
un dernokh dem hot men zey avekgenumen.

00:25:30.519 --> 00:25:33.585
un nisht tsurikgebrengt. a shokhnte,

00:25:34.822 --> 00:25:38.245
zeyer a fayne froy, a goyte,

00:25:38.245 --> 00:25:41.465
aza proste, nisht keyn shtudirte,

00:25:42.449 --> 00:25:47.929
hot genumen a tikhl ire, a groyse, a shal,

00:25:49.081 --> 00:25:53.194
un in zayt fun shal,

00:25:54.616 --> 00:25:57.379
hot zi arayngeneyt gelt.

00:25:58.447 --> 00:26:02.998
az efsher kumt on ergets tsu mayn shvester

00:26:03.813 --> 00:26:08.246
zol zi ober z-, zey zenen geven aynfarshtanen.

00:26:09.213 --> 00:26:14.574
az zi zol, fun dort, az zi hot dort gelt.

00:26:15.507 --> 00:26:19.670
ober men hot nisht gelozt. zi hot es, di shal,

00:26:19.743 --> 00:26:24.294
arayngetrogn in geto, far mayn shvester.

00:26:25.734 --> 00:26:29.458
un me hot ir tsurikgevorfn der shal.

00:26:29.969 --> 00:26:35.128
un nokh dem, nokh mitog, hot zi gebakn broyt, dey goyte,

00:26:35.707 --> 00:26:40.123
un zi hot arayngeton in broyt

00:26:41.343 --> 00:26:46.772
farn bakn, in BATSEK, hot zi arayngeton gelt.

00:26:48.093 --> 00:26:53.893
un dos hot men oykh nisht erloybt, me hot es tsurikgevorfn far der goyte.

00:26:54.657 --> 00:26:59.951
azoy az zi iz avek mit ir kinder on a pitsl esn.

00:27:02.352 --> 00:27:04.136
un dos iz geven...

00:27:06.149 --> 00:27:07.815
vi zent ir geven

00:27:08.748 --> 00:27:10.852
in dey tsaytn?

00:27:09.344 --> 00:27:10.876
in dey tsaytn?

00:27:12.039 --> 00:27:13.519
in der tsayt?

00:27:13.557 --> 00:27:15.206
in Bukarest.

00:27:16.595 --> 00:27:19.543
in velkhe yor zent ir gekumen tsu Bukarest?

00:27:21.252 --> 00:27:23.697
dos ken ikh nisht gedenken.

00:27:24.948 --> 00:27:26.765
ikh ken nisht gedenken.

00:27:27.699 --> 00:27:30.157
se iz aza ruml geven,

00:27:31.293 --> 00:27:34.376
az der mentshn hot zikh nisht gegebn kheshbn.

00:27:36.659 --> 00:27:38.612
vu zent ir geven dort?

00:27:39.099 --> 00:27:39.995
vi azoy?

00:27:39.956 --> 00:27:42.797
bay vemen zent ir geven in Bukarest?

00:27:44.135 --> 00:27:54.052
koydem, a khaverte hot gezogt ikh zol mikh nisht azoy shtark plogn.

00:27:54.496 --> 00:27:57.630
ikh zol kumen mit ir in Bukarest,

00:27:59.154 --> 00:28:02.540
un, zogt zi, "mir ho'mir zen vos ven zayn."

00:28:02.917 --> 00:28:07.198
mir ho'mir gehat a bisele gelt. rumenish gelt.

00:28:07.473 --> 00:28:10.168
yetst vet men zikh opshteln oyf a por minut.
